settings.heading: Do you have minimum quantities on Embroidery?
settings.row_content: Yes, we have a minimum of 6 pieces for embroidery. You can combine any type of top (t-shirts, hoodies, jackets, etc.). Hats are accounted for separately.

settings.heading: Do you have minimum quantities on Screen Printing?
settings.row_content: Yes, we have a minimum of 24 pieces for screen printing. (Restrictions apply. Call for details 302-999-0562).

settings.heading: Do you have minimum quantites on Promotional Products?
settings.row_content: Yes, minimum quantities vary by item. Please call for details. 302-999-0562

settings.heading: What is your turn-around time?
settings.row_content: We typically have a turn around time of 5-10 days, but please give us a call to verify current turn around time.

settings.heading: Do you offer free estimates?
settings.row_content: Yes, please give us a call! 302-999-0562

settings.heading: What forms of payment do you accept?
settings.row_content: We accept all major credit cards, checks, and cash.

settings.heading: What items can you embroider?
settings.row_content:
Anything we can secure in our embroidery hoops can be embroidered. Here are just a few of our most commonly embroidered items:

Towels, Blankets, Sheets, Pillow Cases, Pillow Shams, Shower Curtains, Baby Blankets, Lovie Blanket™, Personalizeable Pals™: Messenger Bags, Tote Bags, Back Packs, Brief Cases, Hats, Coats, Sport Shirts, Dress Shirts, Tee Shirts, Sweat Shirts, Shorts, Sweat Pants, Warm-Up Suits, Jackets, Coats, Christmas Stockings…..

settings.heading: Can I bring in my own goods for embroidery or screen printing?
settings.row_content: Yes, IY will gladly embroider or screen print customer supplied goods. (Note: some restrictions apply. For details, call 302-999-0562 or email info@iyincde.com)

settings.heading: Can I buy goods from you?
settings.row_content: Yes, IY has thousands of items available. Please visit our online catalogs or give us a call to schedule an appointment to visit our showroom to see some of our top sellers.

settings.heading: What design, logo, and art file formats do you accept?
settings.row_content: For embroidery, we accept .jpeg and .pdf format designs. For screen printing and promotional products we require vector artwork (.eps). Please email your artwork to info@iyincde.com.

settings.heading: Can you create a design or logo for me?
settings.row_content: Yes, we have thousands of stock designs available that can be customized for your needs. Browse our design library catalog. We also have a graphic designer available to create your perfect design or logo from scratch. (Note: Set-up / art charges may apply)

settings.heading: Do you provide shipping services?
settings.row_content: Yes, IY can ship your order via UPS anywhere in the continental U.S. (Note: Shipping charges may apply)

settings.heading: Can I dropship my goods to your shop for decoration?
settings.row_content:
Yes, drop ship your order to:

Initially Yours, Inc.
1412 Kirkwood Highway
Wilmington DE 19805

Please note, processing charges may apply.

settings.heading: When are you open?
settings.row_content: We are open by appointment only. Our appointment hours are Monday-Thursday from 9am-3pm.
